<dl id="n12185g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12185g">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12185g"> 185(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> if I &mdash; riotously, the punish / is sorer</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">17. My prowess in his banqueting hall has been punished by draughts of sorrow; <mark>if I have lived riotously, O God, the punishment is sorer</mark> <small> Osborne Bergin, &ldquo;Unpublished Irish Poems&rdquo; <a name="UIRP" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#UIRP"><cite title="source">Studies</cite></a> (March 1924) 90</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
